3. **Adapters** - Infrastructure ready
   - MongoDBAdapter (75% coverage)
   - PostgreSQLAdapter (78% coverage)
   - RedisCacheAdapter

4. **GDPR Methods** - All 7 articles implemented
   - requestDataAccess()
   - rectifyPersonalData()
   - erasePersonalData()
